# UI Text Cleanup Plan: Remove IRC-Style Formatting

## Goal
Replace all IRC-inspired text patterns with clean, sentence case text for better readability.

## Pattern Transformations

| IRC Pattern | Clean Replacement |
|------------|------------------|
| `[ 11 MODULES ]` | `11 Modules` |
| `/SKILLS` | `Skills` |
| `/PROVIDER_MODEL_ID` | `Model` |
| `[ NO_DATA_AVAILABLE ]` | `No data available` |
| `[01] PROVIDER_SUMMARY` | `Provider Summary` |
| `[ SYNCING_NODES... ]` | `Syncing...` |
| `*** /skillName` | Just the skill name |
| `[ADD]`, `[CANCEL]` | `Add`, `Cancel` |
| `PASTE_KEY...` | `Paste key...` |

## Files to Modify

### 1. UsageSidebar.tsx (~35 changes)
- Header: `/RESOURCE_LEDGER` → `Resource Usage`
- Stats: `[ REQ:X ]` → `Requests: X`
- Section headers: `[01] PROVIDER_SUMMARY` → `Provider Summary`
- Table headers: `/PROVIDER`, `/REQUESTS`, etc. → `Provider`, `Requests`, etc.
- Empty states: `[ NO_DATA_AVAILABLE ]` → `No data available`
- Loading: `/GATHERING_USAGE_DATA` → `Loading usage data...`

### 2. SettingsSidebar.tsx (~40 changes)
- Section headers: `/PROVIDER_CONFIG` → `Provider Configuration`
- Categories: `/CLOUD`, `/LOCAL`, `/CUSTOM` → `Cloud`, `Local`, `Custom`
- Buttons: `[ADD]`, `[CANCEL]`, `[DELETE]` → `Add`, `Cancel`, `Delete`
- Status: `[ON]`, `[OFF]` → `On`, `Off`
- Fields: `/AUTH_TOKEN` → `API Key`
- Placeholders: `PASTE_KEY...` → `Paste key...`
- Toggles: `/AUTO_COMPACTION` → `Auto-compact conversations`
- Security: `/UNRESTRICTED_EXECUTION` → `Unrestricted execution`

### 3. SkillsSidebar.tsx (~15 changes)
- Header: `/SKILLS` → `Skills`
- Count: `[ 11 MODULES ]` → `11 modules`
- Column: `/SKILL_ID` → `Skill`
- Loading: `[ SYNCING_NODES... ]` → `Loading skills...`
- Empty: `[ NO_ACTIVE_SKILLS_FOUND ]` → `No skills found`
- Context menu: `*** /skillName` → skill name only

### 4. TriggersSidebar.tsx (~15 changes)
- Header: `/TRIGGERS` → `Triggers`
- Count: `[ 0 SOURCES ]` → `0 triggers`
- Column: `/TRIGGER_ID` → `Trigger`
- Loading: `[ SCANNING_SYSTEM... ]` → `Loading triggers...`
- Empty: `[ NO_TRIGGERS_FOUND ]` → `No triggers found`

### 5. ToolApproval.tsx (~4 changes)
- Header: `/PERMISSION_REQUIRED` → `Permission Required`
- Buttons: `[ ALLOW ]` → `Allow`, `[ REJECT ]` → `Reject`

### 6. SecretRequest.tsx (~6 changes)
- Header: `/SECRET_INPUTS_REQUIRED` → `Secret Required`
- Status text: clean up caps formatting
- Buttons: `[ SAVE_AND_CONTINUE ]` → `Save and Continue`

### 7. InlineScopeProposal.tsx (~1 change)
- Header: `/PLAN_UPDATE` → `Plan Update`

## Implementation Order
1. UsageSidebar.tsx (most visible, user mentioned specifically)
2. SkillsSidebar.tsx (user mentioned `/CALENDAR` example)
3. SettingsSidebar.tsx (largest file)
4. TriggersSidebar.tsx
5. ToolApproval.tsx
6. SecretRequest.tsx
7. InlineScopeProposal.tsx

## Notes
- Keep styling classes intact, only change text content
- Maintain semantic meaning while making text human-readable
- Use sentence case consistently (capitalize first word only, except proper nouns)
